# Anvil SQLite DBs are committed (~820KB total) so each cron run sees
# both pricing.sqlite + mlperf.sqlite — landing card needs both DBs to
# render correctly. Without this, the daily-pricing cron clobbers the
# weekly-mlperf cron's freshness state on the landing card and vice
# versa. Each cron updates only its own DB; the other persists in git.
# Originally gitignored — see commit 0bb70dd's predecessor for context.
